    "All the programs are implemented using PyTorch library.",
    "DatasetA research team with members from \"Qatar University, Doha, Qatar\" and members from \"University of Dhaka, Bangladesh\" and other members from nations like Pakistan and Malaysia are joined and worked together with the doctors.",
    "Initially, they released CXR images for 3classes -COVID (219), normal (1341) and viral pneumonia (1345).",
    "Next its updated with a total of 1200 images of class COVID and added a new class -Lung Opacity (6012) with Normal (10192), COVID (3616) and Viral Pneumonia (1345).",
    "These images are of 299*299 resolution in PNG format [11, 12]."
